title: Does Bindi Irwin#039;s quot;Big Brotherquot; Derek Hough Approve of Her Boyfriend Chandler Powell?l
text:
24 Oct 2015 02:42 PM EST 
Big brother vs. boyfriend, it's a battle many girls have fretted over in the past. Fortunately for Bindi Irwin , her "big brother" Dancing With the Stars ' partner Derek Hough is quite the fan of her man, Chandler Powell ! News chatted with the pair during a rehearsal break on Friday in Los Angeles, where Derek said he totally approves of Bindi's BF. as Bindi cheered next to him, excited to get the seal of approval from her "big brother."
